Job Details - Senior HR Manager - Retail
Senior HR Manager - Retail
Dinsdag 6 mei 2014
Description
An exciting opportunity for a Senior HR Manager has arisen within a diversified local company in Dubai.
It is a diverse organisation with a matrix reporting style. This is an operational role, reporting to the HRBP, for the retail side of the business.
This is a generalist role so will require a strong understanding of all pillars of HR.
You will need to understand policies and procedures and be able to coach and support line managers.You will need to be Arabic speaking as well as English with regional experience.}
Job Reference:RJMW015813
Position Type:Permanent
Sector:Human Resources, Retail/Wholesale
Job Duration:n/a
Working Hours:Full-time
Location:Dubai, United Arab Emirates
Salary:£68,000 - £88,000 per year
Contact:Rebecca Morecroft, Contact Code: PO Box 125115, Digby Morgan, Digby Morgan (DIFC) Limited, United Arab Emirates
Phone / Fax:971 (0) 4 401 9196 / 44 (0)20 7495 4474
